data.description: Gorgeous home in family friendly neighborhood. HOA maintains green spaces, neighborhood park/playground, work out facility and swimming pool. This home offers beautiful wood floors in living and office. Office has patio access. Second living could be sunroom. The gourmet kitchen offers granite counters, lots of cabinet space and double ovens. Two dining areas with a butler's pantry. The utility room is large and has lots of cabinet and counter space with mud area. Bonus room upstairs. Lots of built-ins throughout. Must see!
